&lt;p&gt;This is a 20-hour-per-week contract role well suited for someone who enjoys a mix of marketing coordination, content support, relationship management, and operational follow-through.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hourly Rate: $30 to $40&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
